snippet.title: Amber Heard Replies To Johnny Depp Fans On Twitter
snippet.description:
After Amber Heard responded to Johnny Depp fans on Twitter following his latest loss in court, Roz Weston, Graeme O'Neil and guest co-host Elamin Abdelmahmoud react during ET Canada Live.
